        doParallel (>= 1.0.10), foreach (>= 1.4.3), coda (>= 0.19.1)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, RcppProgress
Imports: parallel, gtools
SystemRequirements: GNU make
Suggests: knitr, MCMCpack, rmarkdown, RColorBrewer, reshape2
